OL,3,CWelsh Water to pay millions over
OL,4,C'serious and unacceptable' failures
OL,6,FWelsh Water is set to pay a proposed
OL,7,F#44.7 million after the industry
OL,8,Fregulator found "serious and
OL,9,Funacceptable" breaches in the
OL,10,Fsupplier's sewage and network services.
OL,12,FOfwat said the supplier failed to
OL,13,Fproperly operate, maintain and upgrade
OL,14,Fits wastewater network to ensure it
OL,15,Fcould cope with levels of sewage and
OL,16,Fwastewater, and did not have adequate
OL,17,Fprocesses in place or oversight by
OL,18,Fsenior bosses.
OL,26,@pD@QOUqD@MO]
