OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773436324
OL,3,CWelsh Water to pay millions over
OL,4,C'serious and unacceptable' failures
OL,6,FOfwat said the planned enforcement
OL,7,Fpackage will include #40.6 million to
OL,8,Freduce spills at specific overflows
OL,9,Fand reduce the environmental damage
OL,10,Fcaused, tackle groundwater entering
OL,11,Fthe sewer network, as well as an extra
OL,12,F#4.1 million to improve river quality
OL,13,Fin "extremely sensitive catchments".
OL,26,@uD@DOUuD@cO]
