FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773436324
OL,3,CWelsh Water to pay millions over
OL,4,C'serious and unacceptable' failures
OL,6,FLynn Parker, senior director for
OL,7,Fenforcement at Ofwat, said: "Our
OL,8,Finvestigation has found serious and
OL,9,Funacceptable breaches in how Dwr Cymru
OL,10,FWelsh Water has operated and
OL,11,Fmaintained its sewage works and
OL,12,Fnetworks, which has resulted in
OL,13,Fexcessive spills from storm overflows
OL,14,Fto the environment.
OL,16,F"We now expect them to focus on
OL,17,Fputting things right so that customers
OL,18,Fcan regain trust in their water
OL,19,Fcompany and the critical service they
OL,20,Fprovide.
OL,26,@oD@]OUxD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
