OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773436324
OL,3,CWelsh Water to pay millions over
OL,4,C'serious and unacceptable' failures
OL,6,F"We understand that the public wants
OL,7,Fto see transformative change.
OL,9,F"That is why we are prioritising this
OL,10,Fsector-wide investigation, which is
OL,11,Fholding companies, like Welsh Water,
OL,12,Fto account."
OL,14,FOfwat stressed the package is more
OL,15,Fthan would otherwise have been paid if
OL,16,FOfwat was to fine the firm ` which
OL,17,Fwould have been #40 million.
OL,19,FIt will now consult on the proposed
OL,20,Fenforcement package, with a deadline
OL,21,Ffor responses of 2 April.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUtD@LO]
