PN,46305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1773436324
OL,3,CWelsh Water to pay millions over
OL,4,C'serious and unacceptable' failures
OL,6,FA Welsh Water spokesperson said: "We
OL,7,Faccept the findings of Ofwat's
OL,8,Finvestigation and apologise for where
OL,9,Fwe have fallen short of the standards
OL,10,Fthat our customers and regulators
OL,11,Frightly expect from us.
OL,13,F"We have started a major
OL,14,Ftransformation programme across the
OL,15,Fcompany, including within our
OL,16,Fwastewater services, focused on
OL,17,Fimproving performance, strengthening
OL,18,Foperational oversight and accelerating
OL,19,Finvestment to deliver better outcomes
OL,20,Ffor rivers and coastal waters.
OL,26,@nD@bOUuD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
